arStrings.szText: (PH) Your Maximum Allegiance is increased by {c_number}[{SF_0}*100|x%|]{/c} and all Allegiance Generation is increased by {c_number}[{SF_1}*100|x%|]{/c}.

(PH) While {c_important}Invoke{/c} is active, your Maximum Allegiance is increased by {c_number}[{SF_2}*100|%x|]{/c}.  {c_number}[{SF_3}*100|%|]{/c} of incoming damage is nullified at the cost of  {c_number}{SF_4}{/c} Allegiance.

(PH) Allegiance decays twice as slowly while {c_important}Invoke{/c} is active and can be used to cast any {c_important}Mobility{/c}, {c_important}Control{/c}, {c_important}Defensive{/c}, or {c_important}Potency{/c} Skill at the cost of {c_number}{SF_5}{/c} Allegiance.
